{"an4.19:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.19 ","an4.19:0.2":"2. Caravagga ","an4.19:0.3":"Tatiyaagatisutta ","an4.19:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, agatigamanani. ","an4.19:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.19:1.3":"Chandagatim gacchati, dosagatim gacchati, mohagatim gacchati, bhayagatim gacchati—","an4.19:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari agatigamanani. ","an4.19:2.1":"Cattarimani, bhikkhave, nagatigamanani. ","an4.19:2.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.19:2.3":"Na chandagatim gacchati, na dosagatim gacchati, na mohagatim gacchati, na bhayagatim gacchati—","an4.19:2.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari nagatigamananiti. ","an4.19:3.1":"Chanda dosa bhaya moha, ","an4.19:3.2":"yo dhammam ativattati; ","an4.19:3.3":"Nihiyati tassa yaso, ","an4.19:3.4":"kalapakkheva candima. ","an4.19:4.1":"Chanda dosa bhaya moha, ","an4.19:4.2":"yo dhammam nativattati; ","an4.19:4.3":"Apurati tassa yaso, ","an4.19:4.4":"sukkapakkheva candima”ti. ","an4.19:4.5":"Navamam. "}